{"type": "article", "id": 10162, "title": "「 儿童节可以准备起来了」之 3D 编织塑料", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-29T07:20:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235620gVYOpZlEGKUvn8RX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t塑料公司 The Keter Group 最近推出了一项新技术，可以生产出柔软的 3D 编织外形。这些看起来柔软的编织外表实际上是注射成型的塑料作品，目前公司推出的这一系列作品是各种颜色的盆栽，花盆外面像是穿了一层小毛衣，是不是很像小时候常见的妈妈的手工？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235616vbJ0U5Ii3Xz8f6ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356162n4QMvZVHR5US3FX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.14914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235617M87qJzmZjEXc34l0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235617GtJp8demcOINCaB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235617Cq7WetYFroxcuMT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235618Ny74gCn2AOpFM6ex.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.95843521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235618l49w1VatC0OEiJ8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.22249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356198wH1BxhGuCgtWFsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.98410758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235619LJXbKOvk43pgjafN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}